= ConsoleKit =

[[Software/ConsoleKit|ConsoleKit]] is a framework for defining and tracking users, login sessions, and seats.

||<#FF8080> ConsoleKit is currently not actively maintained. The focus has shifted to the built-in seat/user/session management of [[Software/systemd]] called [[http://0pointer.de/public/systemd-man/systemd-loginctl.html|systemd-loginctl]]||

